task.description:
Add a new dataclass to dashboard_sections.py:
@dataclass class ObservabilityDashboardSection: """Observability status for the Everything Dashboard.""" training_active: bool current_epoch: int | None max_epochs: int | None current_val_dice: float | None eta_s: float | None heartbeat_age_s: float | None recent_flow_events: list[dict[str, Any]] stall_detection: dict[str, Any] gpu_status: str # "healthy" | "no_gpu" | "stale"
Add it to EverythingDashboard as an optional field (backward compatible with existing dashboard invocations that do not pass observability data).
